comment: Whiteside (MIA) sets the screen on Carroll (TOR) and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Johnson (MIA) does not dislodge Carroll (TOR) or affect his ability to defend.
Carroll (TOR) maintains legal guarding position and makes incidental contact with Johnson (MIA) following the pump fake that does not affect his post move and shot attempt.
RHH shows that Deng (MIA) maintains legal guarding position and makes incidental contact with DeRozan (TOR) that does not affect his RSBQ.
Deng (MIA) does not give DeRozan (TOR) room to land following the jump shot attempt.
Valanciunas (TOR) and Whiteside (MIA) briefly engage and separate during rebounding.
[Observable in production angle] RATR shows that Valanciunas (TOR) makes contact with the ball while part of it still remains in the cylinder above the basket ring.
Deng (MIA) and Lowry (TOR) make incidental contact with one another during rebounding.
Valanciunas (TOR) sets the screen on Dragic (MIA) and gives him room to avoid the contact.
[Detectable with stop watch] Johnson (MIA) does not inbound the ball within 5 seconds.
After communicating with the Replay Center, the ruling on the court that Wade (MIA) was behind the three point line on his field goal was upheld.
Valanciunas (TOR) firms up as he sets the screen on Dragic (MIA) and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Dragic (MIA) sets the screen on Carroll (TOR) and gives him room to avoid the contact. After the screen, Carroll and Dragic briefly engage and separate.
Richardson (MIA) allows Lowry (TOR) to land following the jump shot attempt.
Lowry (TOR) firms up as he sets the screen on Deng (MIA) and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Carroll (TOR) makes contact with Johnson's (MIA) arm that affects his shot attempt.
Dragic (MIA) maintains legal guarding position and makes incidental contact with Lowry (TOR) that does not affect his drive to the basket and shot attempt.
Valanciunas (TOR) maintains legal guarding position and cleanly blocks the ball prior to any incidental contact with Whiteside's (MIA) arm.
Valanciunas (TOR) extends his leg as he sets the screen on Dragic (MIA) without giving him room to avoid the contact.
Wade (MIA) legally contests the jump shot and allows Carroll (TOR) to land following the shot attempt.
Whiteside (MIA) sets the screen on Joseph (TOR) and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Joseph (TOR) maintains legal guarding position and makes incidental contact with Johnson (MIA) after the release that does not affect his drive to the basket and shot attempt.
Whiteside (MIA) gains possession and is able to attempt a controlled pass. The shot clock is correctly reset.
Dragic (MIA) makes contact with Carroll's (TOR) arms that affects his driving shot attempt.
Dragic (MIA) sets the screen on DeRozan (TOR) and gives him room to avoid the contact.
LHH shows that Joseph (TOR) and Carroll (TOR) maintain legal guarding position and make incidental contact with Johnson (MIA) that does not affect his drive to the basket and shot attempt.
Deng (MIA) maintains legal guarding position and makes incidental contact with Carroll (TOR) that does not affect his drive to the basket and shot attempt.
Richardson (MIA) momentarily clenches Lowry's (TOR) jersey, but does not affect his movement or ability to defend Wade (MIA).
Lowry (TOR) makes contact with Wade's (MIA) arm that causes him to lose control of the ball.
Green (MIA) commits a take foul on Joseph (TOR).
Powell (TOR) and Wade (MIA) briefly engage and separate during the inbounds play.
[Detectable with stop watch] Deng (MIA) does not inbound the ball within 5 seconds.
Carroll (TOR) is the last player to touch the ball prior to it going OOB.

After communicating with the Replay Center, there was conclusive video evidence that showed that the ball was last touched by Carroll (TOR) prior to going OOB. The ruling on the court was overturned and Miami was awarded possession.
Johnson (MIA) does not dislodge Joseph (TOR) or affect his ability to defend.
Johnson (MIA) ends his dribble, then fumbles the ball, and picks it up without dribbling again.
Richardson (MIA) commits a take foul on DeRozan (TOR).
Richardson (MIA) commits a take foul on Lowry (TOR).
